            "text": "When evaluating AI models for production APIs, understanding the nuances between ACE-Step 1.5 Turbo and OpenAI offerings is critical for informed decision-making. This post provides actionable insights for API teams, focusing on technical specifications, integration patterns, and performance metrics without unnecessary fluff."
