            "text": "Authorization: Bearer <key>",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " headers. OpenAI’s API follows a comparable pattern but includes additional endpoints for fine-tuning and embeddings. Both support OAuth 2.0 for enterprise integrations, but ACE-Step provides built-in key rotation without downtime, a feature requiring custom implementation in OpenAI’s ecosystem."
