            "type": "text",
            "text": "ACE-Step demonstrates lower latency and higher throughput in text-generation tasks, making it suitable for real-time applications. However, OpenAI’s extended context window benefits document processing workloads. Cost efficiency favors ACE-Step for high-volume use cases, but teams should factor in model capabilities beyond raw metrics."
