            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implement retry logic with exponential backoff for both APIs, as rate limits (e.g., ACE-Step’s 1000 RPM default) can trigger 429 errors. Use idempotency keys for POST requests to prevent duplicate processing. For error handling, ACE-Step returns standardized JSON error codes like "
